<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ʋno na̱ sa yimmi ƲIT59</title>
<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<aka>Christian's Resolution</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋno na̱ sa yimmit
 Chisʋs pulla hoka
 Im antia li mak ocha
 Hikia li hoke.

[V2]
 Ʋba A̱ki yokʋt
 Sa hoho̱yo hoka
 Holitoblit waka̱ya lish
 Immi toba lashke.

[V3]
 Sai okcha̱ya ta̱klʋt,
 Ʋba A̱ki yoka
 Sa chu̱kʋsh oka mominchit
 Ima li pullashke.

[V4]
 Okla e moma kʋt
 Chisʋs pulla hoka
 Anukchetot, holitoblit,
 Iloh aiashashke.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>59</hymn_number>
</song>